      "text": [
        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"كُلُّ يَمِينٍ لاَ يُرَادُ بِهَا وَجْهُ اَللَّهِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ فَلَيْسَ بِشَيْءٍ، فِي طَلاَقٍ أَوْ عِتْقٍ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4291 - Imam (as) said: \"Any oath that is not intended for the sake of Allah (swt), the Almighty and Glorious, is of no consequence, whether it pertains to divorce or emancipation.\""
        ]
      }
    },
